function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	-- The Horadrim Transform into Elites
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	tHoradrimPhantoms = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSceneManager, "VISION_MINIONS")
	
	for i, idHoradrimPhantom in ipairs(tHoradrimPhantoms) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idHoradrimPhantom, sTransformEffectIn)
		Hydra.Wait(0.15)
		local idEliteDemonSpawner = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idHoradrimPhantom)[1]
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idEliteDemonSpawner, false)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idHoradrimPhantom)
	end

end

function Start()	

	--Get andariel spawners ready
	idAndarielFirst = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSceneManager, "ANDARIEL_FIRST")[1]
	idPhantomTaissa = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSceneManager, "VISION_TAISSA")[1]
	followerTaissa = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Taissa_Witch_Follower")
	
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(sConvo_Taissa04, followerTaissa)
	
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(sConvo_Taissa04)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idPhantomTaissa, sFX_AndarielSummon)
	
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idPhantomTaissa,1)
	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(idAndarielFirst)

end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

	--Set HP cap to juuuuust under 80% so we cna be sure the "Andy hits 80%" callback fires
	Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(idActorSpawned, 0.79)
	
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)

	-- Andariel purposely has way way more HP than a normal boss.
	-- Getting her to 80% should feel like getting a regular boss to 50% or so
	
	idActorPlayer = Hydra.PlayerActors()[1]
	followerTaissa = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Taissa_Witch_Follower") 
	
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerTaissa)
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(followerTaissa)
	
	-- Let player keep damaging Andy but prevent the 60% callback from firing
	-- until the conversation has started
	Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(idActor, 0.62)
	
	-- Spawn two chain pillars on either side of followerTaissa that chain her
	-- If anyone destroys a pillar, a replacement spawns immediately and re-chains Taissa
	--Hydra.QActorPower(idActor, Andariel_Pillar,  followerTaissa);
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(followerTaissa, "GenericPhasedAnimation", 0)
	
	-- Taissa and Player say VO line
	
	Hydra.Wait(3)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorPlayer) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerTaissa) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(sConvo_Taissa05, idActorPlayer, followerTaissa)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(idActor, 0.59)
	
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)
	
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(sConvo_Taissa05)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(sConvo_Taissa06, followerTaissa)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(sConvo_Taissa06)
	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(followerTaissa)
	Hydra.QActorPower(followerTaissa, Taissa_BreakFree, idActor)

	
	-- The chain pillars are killed as Taissa does the yell anim
	-- At the same time, Andariel goes into her stagger anim, 
	-- turns off her AI, and becomes untargetable and invulnerable.
	
	Hydra.ActorFaceActor(followerTaissa, idActor)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerTaissa)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(sConvo_Taissa07, followerTaissa)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(sConvo_Taissa07)
	
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idActor)
	idRewardLocation = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(sRewardDropActor, idActor)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idActor, fxAndarielLaugh)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idActor, 2)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerTaissa, idRunTo, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerTaissa, idRunTo)
	Hydra.QActorDelete(followerTaissa)

	
	-- Drop boss loot after Andariel vanishes
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	--Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerTaissa)
	Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActor(idRewardLocation, "Dungeon_Boss_Items")

	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerTaissa)
	Hydra.SetGameVariableFlag("QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_03_DungeonExitPortal", true)
	Hydra.EventSend("AndarielEchoDefeated")
	
	

end

szUserFunctionsScript:
------------------------------------------------------------
-- This is a shared function with all "Find Scene" phases
function UF_AccompanyTaissaToScene(idActor, idTrigger)
	-- Set the new Scene Manager
	idSceneManager = idTrigger
	
	-- Find the Relative RUnTo Spot, Q Follower Taissa to Move there
	local idRunTo = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSceneManager, "GOTO_TAISSA_01")[1]
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActor, idRunTo, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idActor, idTrigger)
	Hydra.QActorDelete(idActor)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idActor)
	
	-- Create a Quest Taissa at the position of Follower Taissa, set Follower Taissa to invisible
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idRunTo)
	idQuestTaissa = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(sNonCombatTaissa, idActor, false, 0, 0)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idActor, true)
end

------------------------------------------------------------
-- This is a shared function with the Arcanum/Temple "SpeakTaissa" phases
function UF_PhantomSceneTransform()
	-- Grab the right Phantom Actors from current Temple Manager
	idPhantomAndariel = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSceneManager, "VISION_ANDARIEL")[1]
	idPhantomTaissa = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSceneManager, "VISION_TAISSA")[1]
	
	-- Play the VFX
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idPhantomTaissa, sFX_AndarielSummon)
	
	--Delete Taissa/Andariel
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idPhantomTaissa,1)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idPhantomAndariel, 1)
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	-- Grab Fight Actors
	tPhantoms = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSceneManager, "VISION_MINIONS")
	idPhantomBoss = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSceneManager, "VISION_BOSS")[1]
	
	-- Convert every trash mob into a demon
	for i, idPhantom in ipairs (tPhantoms) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idPhantom, sTransformEffectIn)
		Hydra.Wait(0.15)
		local idDemonSpawner = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idPhantom)[1]
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idDemonSpawner, false)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idPhantom)
	end
	
	--Convert the Boss Mob into an elite
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idPhantomBoss, sTransformEffectIn)
	local idDemonSpawner = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idPhantomBoss)[1]
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idDemonSpawner, false)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idPhantomBoss)

	-- Delete Quest Taissa (replaced witha  Follower in the upcoming phase)
	--Hydra.ActorDelete(idQuestTaissa)
end

------------------------------------------------------------
-- This is a shared function with all moments where a Portal Candle is enabled
function UF_EnableNextPortal()
	-- Enable the Portal Actor linked to the Scene Managaer
	idPortal = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSceneManager, "VISION_PORTAL")[1]
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idPortal)
end
